        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6 rounded-md text-center hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Personal Portfolio</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">The website you're on right now! Built with Astro, Tailwind, and TypeScript.</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/shivmishra76/portfolio-website" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">View Project</a>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6 rounded-md text-center hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Satellite Tracker CLI</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">A command-line tool to track satellites in real-time. It fetches TLE data, calculates orbital positions, and determines visibility from any ground station on Earth.</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/shivmishra76/sat-tracker-cli" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">View Project</a>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6 rounded-md text-center hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors">
